{
  "texts": [
    "Shahzad et al. (2020) find distinctive safe haven and hedge properties of Bitcoin and gold in G7 stock markets.",
    "Bouri et al. (2020a) find evidence that Bitcoin, Ripple, and Stellar are safe havens for US equity indices, whereas Monero and Litecoin do so for the US equity market index.",
    "Bitcoin has the least dependence on other assets and a superior safe-haven ability compared to gold and commodities (Bouri et al. 2020b).",
    "Recently, investor concerns over the COVID-19 outbreak have led to research on the role of Bitcoin as a safe haven asset.",
    "Corbet et al. (2020a) find that investors are more inclined to view digital currency as a safe haven."
  ]
}